#: ../../source/vuln/xss/trick/rpo.rst:2
msgid "RPO(Relative Path Overwrite)"
msgstr "RPO (Relative Path Overwrite)"

#: ../../source/vuln/xss/trick/rpo.rst:4
msgid ""
"RPO(Relative Path Overwrite) 攻击又称为相对路径覆盖攻击，依赖于浏览器和网络服务器的反应，利用服务器的 Web "
"缓存技术和配置差异。"
msgstr ""
"An RPO (Relative Path Overwrite) attack, also known as a relative path "
"overwrite attack, depends on browser and web server behavior and exploits web "
"cache techniques and configuration differences on the server."
